{"timestamp": "2026-06-27T16:25:34.874061+00:00", "role": "tutor", "raw_response": {"id": "ffk_asbeI-Oq1MkPkqSE2AE", "created": 1782577533, "model": "gemini-2.5-pro", "object": "chat.completion", "system_fingerprint": null, "choices": [{"finish_reason": "stop", "index": 0, "message": {"content": "嗯，听起来是这样。如果树是从土壤里“吃”东西长大的，那土壤肯定会变少。\n\n实际上，在17世纪，一位名叫范·海尔蒙特的科学家也跟你想的一样。他做了一个实验来验证这个想法。你猜实验结果是什么？", "role": "assistant", "tool_calls": null, "function_call": null, "images": [], "thinking_blocks": []}}], "usage": {"completion_tokens": 64, "prompt_tokens": 532, "total_tokens": 596, "completion_tokens_details": {"text_tokens": 64}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": null, "text_tokens": 532, "image_tokens": null, "video_tokens": null}, "cache_read_input_tokens": null}, "vertex_ai_grounding_metadata": [], "vertex_ai_url_context_metadata": [], "vertex_ai_safety_results": [], "vertex_ai_citation_metadata": [], "service_tier": "default"}}
